Acked-by: Vaibhav Hiremath <vaibhav.hiremath@linaro.org>
Acked-by: Hans Verkuil <hans.verkuil@cisco.com>
Signed-off-by: Mauro Carvalho Chehab <mchehab@osg.samsung.com>

